message.body: Hunter has some fresh forged chicken mushrooms for you!
He just said call Bruce. I have chickens for him. I was confused.
That's awesome! We're camping until sunday, but we could come get them then. I hope that's not too long for them to be good.
They might not last that long but he will get you more! Hav fun camping! I'm jealous!
I'd love to go along on the more gathering if that's possible, timing-wise.
Yes!! We can do a weekend forage!
